<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div>
<p class="p1" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">&nbsp;</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary&nbsp;</font><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">attention which affects your children.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of head lice in a pupil in one of our&nbsp;</font><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">Year 1 classes. Head lice are common amongst young children at school. They are spread through&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">head-to-head contact. They may cause discomfort and itchiness of the scalp but can be easily treated&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">with special shampoos and combs, which are available at most pharmacies.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">We are taking all precautions necessary at school including regularly checking all pupils for head lice.&nbsp;</font><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">We will be in touch with the parents of any child we suspect of having head lice. Please note that head&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">lice may spread within a family, so please make sure you undertake any necessary checks at home,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">especially among young siblings.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">For further information about head lice and how best to treat them, please <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Head-lice/Pages/Introduction.aspx">follow this link</a>.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Warm regards,</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Alison Mackey</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Deputy Head of Primary</font></p>
